title: control.ipAddress is now window.ipAddress... for some reason control.ipAddress…
message: control.ipAddress is now window.ipAddress... for some reason control.ipAddress wasn't getting set right. The oscManager.delegate is now reset -before- reading in new json interfaces instead of after. That was a bad bug, since it basically overwrote every delegate unless you set the delegate after the interface was loaded programatically.
